instructions.command_snippet: RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y cur...
instructions.command_all: RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y curl wget && curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_16.x | bash - && apt-get install -y nodejs && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends git openssh-client && npm install -g yarn && apt-get install -y python3.8 python3-pip && update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/pip pip /usr/bin/pip3 1 && update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/bin/python3 1 && update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python3 python3 /usr/bin/python3.8 1 && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/* && adduser pwuser

RUN mkdir /ms-playwright && mkdir /ms-playwright-agent && cd /ms-playwright-agent && npm init -y && npm i /tmp/playwright-core.tar.gz && npx playwright install --with-deps && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/* && rm /tmp/playwright-core.tar.gz && rm -rf /ms-playwright-agent && chmod -R 777 /ms-playwright

RUN mkdir -p /var/run/sshd && \
	apt update && \
	apt install -y openssh-server && \
	apt install -y unzip && \
	chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-entrypoint.sh && \
	export SSH_PUBLIC_KEY="$SSH_PUBLIC_KEY"
instructions.author: Utkarsh Dixit "utkarshdix02@gmail.com"

instructions.command_all:
RUN curl https://johnvansickle.com/ffmpeg/releases/ffmpeg-release-amd64-static.tar.xz -L -o ffmpeg.tar.xz && \
	tar -xf ffmpeg.tar.xz && \
	mv ffmpeg-*-amd64-static/ffmpeg /usr/local/bin/ && \
	rm -rf ffmpeg.tar.xz ffmpeg-*-amd64-static
